    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Baskets or basketlike containers intended primarily for carrying laundry; often oval or rectangular and generally with a pair of handles at the rim.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
